articles.author: Katie Kindelan
articles.title: Prince William steps out solo for wedding of his and Prince Harry's close friend - Good Morning America
articles.description: Prince William and Prince Harry's close friend Hugh Grosvenor, the Duke of Westminster, wed Olivia Henson on June 7. William attended the event solo, without wife Kate.
articles.content:
Prince William on Friday celebrated the marriage of one of his and Prince Harry's closest friends.
